From 99283fd0d6bd5ff1a2c043b27492da9be13ebf2f Mon Sep 17 00:00:00 2001
From: Sarika Sharma <sarishar@qti.qualcomm.com>
Date: Wed, 21 May 2025 10:18:45 +0530
Subject: [PATCH] iw: add support for MLO station dump

Currently, the iw station dump only provides deflink statistics of
associated station. This is sufficient to print non-ML station
statistics but for multi-link (ML) station, it does not print
information for all the links.

Hence, add support to parse nested link attributes for multi-link
operation (MLO) and print link statistics also as part of station dump.

Sample output:

